g.text: •Sn-doped in Mg2Si achieves significant ZT value as p-type of 0.82 at 800 K with concentrations x= 0.6 and x = 0.4 and at Sn concentrations x= 0.2 behaving as n-type, ZT reaches the maximum value of 0.33583.•0.03 at% Al doping in Mg2Si demonstrated a ZT value of 0.325 at 823K.

•ZT value for Li doped Mg2Si gives maximum value for x ≈2 at% is 0.76409 at 400K. •ZT value for Na doped with x ≈2 at% in Mg2Si gives maximum value, Na-doped 0.7697 at 400K, which is quite high as reported for Mg2Si p-type doping yet.
Mg2Si p-type Na and Mg2Si n-type Bi doping elements can be suggested for complete thermoelectric assembly at 500 to 800 K temperature application
